<div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content>
  <p style="text-align:justify;white-space: normal !important;white-space:pre-wrap;" class=""><strong>Co-investments</strong><br>Raspberry has co-invested in 21 startups (and 6 follow ons) since mid-2022. Our areas of interest are ClimateTech and AI. We’ve invested in carbon capture, renewable energy, alternative protein, electric mobility and more. </p>
